    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000846/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """- Understanding the IT sector in the EU: towards digital economy
- Structure of the ICT sector in the EU
- Introduction to the specificities of digital products and services
- Digital marketing
- Early-stage internationalization (comparison with other regions). Where should you locate your company? Role of clusters, co-working spaces and centres for innovation support
- What happens when the product/service is already in the market?"""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/j.franco.riquelme%40upm.es> ;
